    "First, all genes were mapped to their official NCBI gene symbols for Homo sapiens or filtered out.",
    "Gene sets were then converted into vectors with values corresponding to the inverse document frequency (IDF) 49.",
    "Truncated Singular Value Decomposition (Truncated SVD) 50 was then used to reduce the dimensionality of the IDF vectors to the 50 largest singular values."
